article_title: Nobody Has Done More For LGBT Healthcare Than Callen-Lorde Community Health Center

article_metadata.description: A look behind the walls of Callen-Lorde Community Health Center, a primary care center dedicated to providing medical health care to the city's LGBT population without regard to a patient's ability to pay.

og.description: "It’s a home, a health care home.”
og.title: Nobody Has Done More For LGBT Healthcare Than Callen-Lorde Community Health Center
